Get ready for a high-octane D&B cardio session as @cardyac takes charge of Q-Radio’s Cardio Mix series!🚨🚑👨🏾‍⚕️

Cardyac is the moniker of Mumbai-based Moksh Shah. He kickstarted DJing at the early age of 13 and as his influences grew, he found himself drawn to the world of bass music, eventually making it a staple sound in his DJ sets. 🔉⚡️

Tighten those laces and keep the electrolytes ready - @cardyac’s cardio session is now online! 📡🖥️🏃🏽‍♂️

latestPosts.caption:
This one is a real special one. Wrapping up year 10 of this very thing called Cardyac. Young but feels old to say that I’ve been a DJ for a decade at this point. Was a shit DJ 10 years back, still am. Nothing has changed.

Pushing some boundaries, trying new things. Come through for some lush afro alongside a fine lineup of @itsdhiraaj // @mograbazaar with the evergood @groovetherapy.in // @pratikkramchandani at fav @raastabombay rooftop.
Also a bit of success to do a gig with groove therapy after a few attempts🤣

All in all, pull through. The weather is good, the music sure will be good too !

🎫 on Skillbox. Free before 9:30, rest club rules apply
